node.text: Interested in a career where you can be your own boss and entrepreneur? Well, I have an exciting opportunity for you! I spent the day with some of @bhhscalifornia’s top agents learning all about what it takes to become a real estate agent in Southern California. We visited two of their most luxurious listings—and now all Hannah hears me talk about is when we are building our own home sauna. Check out how I spent my day and check my stories for more info on how you can become your own boss, getting out of the 9-5 office life and into some of the best million dollar listings. Shout out to @paigesellssandiego @blumenfeldgroup @patcairnx for showing me the ropes of agent life!

node.text:
Celebrated National Rum Day with none other than @RumHaven & @HannahG11 :)

 We had the best time shaking up our favorite cocktails and learning to make some new ones like the Bright & Sunny ☀️ we’ve been recreating it at home and it's been bringing some serious summer vibes to our at home date nights. #ad #for21+ 

Ingredients:
2.5oz RumHaven
.75 oz Lime Juice
1/8 oz Simple Syrup
2 oz Ginger Beer
2 Dashes Aromatic Bitters
3 Lime Wheels, Slice of Ginger, & Cherry for Garnish
 
Directions: Combine RumHaven, lime juice, and simple syrup and shake lightly with ice. Strain into a Collins glass with lime wheels and fresh ice. Top with ginger beer and add 2 dashes of aromatic bitters. Garnish with ginger slice & cherry.

Club Dylan is so exclusive, only @rumhaven and @hannahg11 could get in 👀 

if you need us, we’ll be mixing up our favorite RumHaven cocktails for National Rum Month. Check out our new favorite recipe below
 #ad #for21+ #RumHaven 

RumHaven's My Slice of Haven:

Ingredients: 
2 oz RumHaven
1 oz Club Soda

Directions: Add ingredients to an ice-filled glass and stir together to combine and chill. Garnish with lime
